item.description: A show is going to be held at the Venus De milo called Laughter is the best medicine! There will be 3 acts: The portuguese fireman, Steve Lopes, and Heidi Foss. (All comedians) This benefit is for the Centers for Cancer Cure. Southcoast hosp. is the sponsor. If you have ques. or want to purchase tickets the number on the flyer is 508-961-5353.Tickets cost $25. I was interested in going so please let me know if you'd like to go too.
item.how_to_find_us: I will wait at the front entrance of the restaraunt
